These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
Game: canasta, snooker, monopoly, bridge
Movie-Genre: action, musical, drama, satire
1. Movie-Genre:musical is on the left of Movie-Genre:action##1
2. Game:canasta == Movie-Genre:satire##1
3. Movie-Genre:drama is on the right of Movie-Genre:action##1
4. Game:snooker is on the left of Movie-Genre:satire##1
5. Game:bridge is on the left of Movie-Genre:action##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Game          | bridge | monopoly | snooker | canasta   |
| Movie-Genre   | musical  | action     | drama   | satire |

