.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
Flower: daffodil, balloon-flower, iris, dahlia
Transport: car, van, boat, tram
1. Flower:dahlia == Transport:van##1
2. Flower:daffodil is on the far right##1
3. Flower:balloon-flower is on the right of Flower:dahlia##1
4. Flower:dahlia is on the right of Transport:boat##1
5. Transport:van is on the left of Transport:car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Flower   | iris | dahlia | balloon-flower | daffodil    |
| Transport   | boat    | van      | car | tram |

